The task is to extract the amount of profit an entity retains after all expenses have been deducted, as indicated in the cash flow statement. This corresponds to the line item that shows the net profit, which is the final profit figure after expenses, interest, taxes, depreciation, and amortization.

From the provided problem table, the relevant line item is:

| Account      | Amount    | Date       |
|--------------|-----------|------------|
| Net Profit   | 1903401.82 | 2024-02-05 |

This value represents the profit retained.
